ynergism, Antagonism', NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/29049/', '[1] King MH, Richards DW "Near syncope and chest tightness after administration of apraclonidine before argon laser iridotomy." Am J Ophthalmol 110 (1990): 308-9[2] Pekdemir M, Yanturali S, Karakus G "More than just an ocular solution." Emerg Med J 22 (2005): 753-4[3] "Product Information. Iopidine (apraclonidine)." Alcon Laboratories Inc, Fort Worth, TX.', 1767363020);
